data.description: Introducing this updated Sante Fe style home with a uniquely situated lot providing spectacular mountain views of the Santa Rosa Mountains from the front and the back. As you enter through the front private courtyard, prepare to be captivated by a glistening pebble tec pool and an elevated spa that promises moments of serenity and relaxation. The exterior boasts a sleek smooth stucco finish that adds to the pristine look. Soaring ceilings, a spacious kitchen with marble countertops, and a living room with a marble tile fireplace allow for seamless flow between the living, dining, kitchen, and backyard dining areas making the home perfect for entertaining. Walk on newly updated, porcelain floors to your primary suite with a sliding door leading to the backyard and a remodeled bathroom equipped with a custom double vanity and meticulously designed, floor-to-ceiling tiled, partial glassed shower. Relax in the backyard and mountain views under the alumawood covered patio and enjoy extra privacy with high, block walls with low maintenance artificial turf and desert landscaping. Excellent location with walking distance to Old Town La Quinta, pickle and tennis courts, and a short distance to hiking trails. Your desert oasis awaits!
